ZH: 我不小心跌倒了。
EN: I accidentally fell down.

ZH: 他从楼梯上跌下来了。
EN: He fell down from the stairs.

ZH: 她踩到了香蕉皮，跌了个四脚朝天。
EN: She stepped on a banana peel and fell flat on her back.

ZH: 孩子们在玩耍时跌倒了。
EN: The kids fell while playing.

ZH: 他在滑冰时跌得很重。
EN: He fell hard while ice skating.

ZH: 小狗跳过障碍时跌倒了。
EN: The puppy fell when jumping over the obstacle.

ZH: 她的腿一抬就跌倒了。
EN: She fell down as soon as she lifted her leg.

ZH: 我的自行车前轮突然跌进了一个坑。
EN: The front wheel of my bicycle suddenly fell into a pothole.

ZH: 他跌了好几次都没有受伤。
EN: He fell several times without getting hurt.

ZH: 雪下得太大了，导致他跌倒了。
EN: The heavy snow caused him to slip and fall.

ZH: 他在冰面上滑行时跌倒了。
EN: He fell while gliding on the ice rink.

ZH: 他冲进房间时脚跌了一下。
EN: His foot slipped when he rushed into the room.

ZH: 森林里的树木很滑，容易跌倒。
EN: The trees in the forest are slippery and easy to fall on.

ZH: 这个小孩学走路时总是跌跌撞撞。
EN: This child always stumbles when learning to walk.

ZH: 他在公园里玩足球时突然跌倒了。
EN: He suddenly fell down while playing football in the park.

ZH: 天黑了，她走路时一不小心跌了个狗吃屎。
EN: It was dark, and she accidentally tripped and fell while walking.

ZH: 长跑时我不小心跌倒了。
EN: I accidentally fell down during the long-distance race.

ZH: 小偷趁乱跌倒在地，被抓住了。
EN: The thief fell to the ground and was caught during the chaos.

ZH: 他一边奔跑一边跌倒了。
EN: He fell down while running.

ZH: 她走路太急，结果跌出了门口。
EN: She walked too quickly and ended up falling out of the doorway.

ZH: 在冰面上行走要小心，以免跌倒。
EN: Be careful when walking on the ice to avoid falling down.
